  "lyrics": "I know there's a way to go right here To live your life inside of fear I feel for you, you're not the only one When the world is low I need you to know that's not the way you'll go Lie, love and positivity, that's wrong I've been waiting for you too long Baby, I've been waiting for you too long You should know by now, you should know by now Well then if you just don't want this, just go away now I've been waiting too long for you in the night Yeah, I've been waiting too long for you to get our song right Make my heart right Yeah, they say follow the light into the dark You'll find, you'll find a way But it's been too long for me, long for you In this disaster inside you seem cold to me, cold to me Is there anything you owe to me in your heart? In your heart I can't take it no more, you can't share me no more It's over at the light way Yeah, you'll run away You've taken too long in this moment You've taken too long, I only get this one life Oh, and I feel it coming on That's what you do Yeah, I feel it coming on You take it away and you've taken too much from me You've taken too much from me, you've taken too much away from me Oh, can't you see? That there's a love life beyond you, love life beyond this Love life beyond you, love life beyond this I can feel you Yeah, your shadow slipping away",
  "lyricsSegments": [
    {
      "end": 18.18000030517578,
      "text": "I know there's a way to go right here To live your life inside of fear",
      "start": 0
    },
    {
      "end": 25.700000762939453,
      "text": "I feel for you, you're not the only one When the world is low",
      "start": 18.280000686645508
    },
    {
      "end": 31.639999389648438,
      "text": "I need you to know that's not the way you'll go",
      "start": 25.700000762939453
    },
    {
      "end": 39.70000076293945,
      "text": "Lie, love and positivity, that's wrong I've been waiting for you too long",
      "start": 33.720001220703125
    },
    {
      "end": 45.400001525878906,
      "text": "Baby, I've been waiting for you too long",
      "start": 40.2599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 51.2400016784668,
      "text": "You should know by now, you should know by now",
      "start": 45.400001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 59.599998474121094,
      "text": "Well then if you just don't want this, just go away now",
      "start": 51.2400016784668
    },
    {
      "end": 63.7599983215332,
      "text": "I've been waiting too long for you in the night",
      "start": 59.900001525878906
    },
    {
      "end": 69.22000122070312,
      "text": "Yeah, I've been waiting too long for you to get our song right",
      "start": 63.7599983215332
    },
    {
      "end": 73.4000015258789,
      "text": "Make my heart right",
      "start": 70.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 77.86000061035156,
      "text": "Yeah, they say follow the light into the dark",
      "start": 74.4000015258789
    },
    {
      "end": 81.31999969482422,
      "text": "You'll find, you'll find a way",
      "start": 77.86000061035156
    },
    {
      "end": 85.95999908447266,
      "text": "But it's been too long for me, long for you",
      "start": 81.31999969482422
    },
    {
      "end": 93.44000244140625,
      "text": "In this disaster inside you seem cold to me, cold to me",
      "start": 85.95999908447266
    },
    {
      "end": 99.05999755859375,
      "text": "Is there anything you owe to me in your heart?",
      "start": 93.44000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 102.41999816894531,
      "text": "In your heart",
      "start": 100.26000213623047
    },
    {
      "end": 108.5999984741211,
      "text": "I can't take it no more, you can't share me no more",
      "start": 103.9800033569336
    },
    {
      "end": 113.55999755859375,
      "text": "It's over at the light way",
      "start": 108.5999984741211
    },
    {
      "end": 118.08000183105469,
      "text": "Yeah, you'll run away",
      "start": 115.0199966430664
    },
    {
      "end": 121.9800033569336,
      "text": "You've taken too long in this moment",
      "start": 118.13999938964844
    },
    {
      "end": 127.94000244140625,
      "text": "You've taken too long, I only get this one life",
      "start": 123.05999755859375
    },
    {
      "end": 133.77999877929688,
      "text": "Oh, and I feel it coming on",
      "start": 127.94000244140625
    },
    {
      "end": 137.1999969482422,
      "text": "That's what you do",
      "start": 133.77999877929688
    },
    {
      "end": 141.05999755859375,
      "text": "Yeah, I feel it coming on",
      "start": 138.0399932861328
